channel.title: Can someone help me with portforwarding issues please?
channel.description:
I have 2 computers, my laptop and my old computer that I used to use to run servers or bot on.
When I portforward on my laptop, it works great. The port is open, etc. But when I try to portforward on my old computer, the ports won't open. I am asking for someone to help me out please.
If you can help please reply ASAP.
